nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars The Complete Season Four

Star Wars: The Clone Wars The Complete Season Four is a three-disc Blu-ray or four-disc DVD set of the 2011–2012 fourth season of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series. It was released by Warner Home Video on October 23, 2012.
